    "The conformal invariance of the theory is described by the vanishing of the stress tensor, with the following contribution from the symplectic bosons and free fermionsT = - 1 2 ϵ αβ: ξ α ∂η β + η α ∂ξ β: + 1 2 ϵ AB: ψ A ∂χ B -χ A ∂ψ B:.",
    "JHEP04(2024)048We will denote the modes of this stress tensor by L n. We could also add contributions from the (b, c) ghost system and the ghosts required for the Z = 0 gauge condition [12]."
